chapters.title: Chapter 8:  Sea Folk and Kin
chapters.info: Garenia Rosoinde, p. 194 (216)—Name used by Zarya Alkaese to disguise her identity as a runaway novice. Born in Saldaea, she came to Ebou Dar years ago, and returned from a trip fairly recently. She has considerable strength in the One Power; she could match Lelaine or Romanda. Vandene recognized her for who she really was. See also Alkaese, Zarya.
